        <p>Founded in 2017, Kraken Technologies develops a revolutionary operating system for the energy sector. Our mission is to transform energy resource management by optimizing renewable energy production and improving the efficiency of decentralized networks. By 2020, we expanded our presence internationally. Today, our technology is used in 17 countries, managing over 54 million customer accounts and supervising 42 GW of contracted power. In 2021, we strengthened our presence in Europe through strategic collaborations with several major energy providers.</p>

