        <p>Positioned on open source and innovation, Makina Corpus has placed the Python language at the core of its technical strategy since its inception. Engaged in the Python community, our experts use this language, combined with other technologies, to develop various web applications: business applications, mapping tools, AI, and Data Science tools, etc.</p>

        <p>Explore our job offers, achievements, and articles at <a href=https://makina-corpus.com>makina-corpus.com</a></p>
